Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:39.75,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fn@FZYouSong GBK 509R\bord0.1\frz270\c&HEBEBEB&\3c&HEBEBEB&\fsp10\pos(1772.492,238.575)}奥勒沃尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:48.00,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fn@FZYouSong GBK 509R\bord0.1\frz270\c&HEBEBEB&\3c&HEBEBEB&\t(7190,8233,\c&H0C0D0C&,\3c&H0C0D0C&)\pos(1863,128)}那里聚集着许许多多的灵魂，\N{\fscy50}\N{\fscy100}我在那儿与往日的战友说上了话。\N{\fscy50}\N{\fscy100}　　　　　　　　　　　　{\fnFZYouSong GBK 509R}—{\fn@FZYouSong GBK 509R}大魔法师伏拉莫{\fnFZYouSong GBK 509R}—
